<div class="calcpad-output">
 <h3>Geometrical Properties of Rectangle</h3>
 <div style="max-width:120mm">
  <img alt="rectangle.png" class="side" src="Images/mechanics/sections/rectangle.png" style="height:150pt;"/>
 </div>
 <p>Dimensions</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>h</var>
   =
   <u class="input-4">2</u>
  </span>
  m,
  <span class="eq">
   <var>b</var>
   =
   <u class="input-4">1</u>
  </span>
  m
 </p>
 <p>Area</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>A</var>
   =
   <var>h</var>
   ·
   <var>b</var>
   = 2 · 1 = 2
  </span>
  m
  <sup>2</sup>
 </p>
 <p>Centroid</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>y</var>
   <sub>c</sub>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    <var>b</var>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    1
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
   = 0.5
  </span>
  m
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>z</var>
   <sub>c</sub>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    <var>h</var>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    2
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    2
   </span>
   = 1
  </span>
  m
 </p>
 <p>Perimeter</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>P</var>
   = 2 ·  (
   <var>h</var>
   +
   <var>b</var>
   )  = 2 ·  ( 2 + 1 )  = 6
  </span>
  m
 </p>
 <p>Second moments of area</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>I</var>
   <sub>y</sub>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    <var>b</var>
    ·
    <var>h</var>
    <sup>3</sup>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    12
   </span>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    1 · 2
    <sup>3</sup>
    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    12
   </span>
   = 0.667
  </span>
  m
  <sup>4</sup>
 </p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>I</var>
   <sub>z</sub>
   =
   <span class="dvc">
    <var>b</var>
    <sup>3</sup>
