    <span class="dvl">
    </span>
    12
   </span>
   = 0.167
  </span>
  m
  <sup>4</sup>
 </p>
 <p>Polar moment of area</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>I</var>
   <sub>x</sub>
   =
   <var>I</var>
   <sub>y</sub>
   +
   <var>I</var>
   <sub>z</sub>
   = 0.667 + 0.167 = 0.833
  </span>
  m
  <sup>4</sup>
 </p>
 <p>Radii of gyration</p>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>r</var>
   <sub>y</sub>
   =
   <span class="o1">
    <span class="r1">
    </span>
    <span class="dvc">
     <var>I</var>
     <sub>y</sub>
     <span class="dvl">
     </span>
     <var>A</var>
    </span>
   </span>
